name: Milking machine
description:
Donate Coffee for Gtonero

This LoRA model was created by Gtonero
v1.4 Increase image training
If the situation is right, the resulting image will be less distorted.

recommend use highres.fix denoising = >0.4

prompt : (milking machine:1.0-1.2), (lactation:1.0-1.2),
If used with other LoRAs, increase str = (lactation) to 1.2

Training Data v.1.4

  • 437 image 5 repeats 4 epochs

  • Powershell ISE run script kohya-ss

  • module = Networks.LoRA

  • cosine_with_restarts 3

  • 8 DIM / 4 Alpha

  • U-net 1e-4
